@#!%PerlProg%
#
# f.unblock - unblock a staff tape, producing the standard format
#
# The f.unblock script is used on the staff tape produced as part of the
# phone book printing.  The f2.unblock is for the dataset produced by
# AISS explicitly for ph.
#
