# Tape layout is as follows:
# 9	SSN				1-9
# 1     pad				10
# 23	last name			11-33
# 15	first name			34-48
# 15	middle name			49-63
# 15	spouse name			64-78
# 75	title				79-153
# 25	department			154-178
# 25	office number			179-203
# 25	office street address		204-228
# 16	office city			229-244
# 2	office state			245-246
# 5	office zip code			247-251
# 3	office mailcode			252-254
# 10	office phone			255-264
# 1	suppress home address (if *)	265
# 50	home street address		266-315
# 15	home city			316-330
# 2	home state			331-332
# 5	home zip code			333-337
# 1	suppress home phone (if *)	338
# 11	home phone number		339-349
# 50	email address (don't use as it's often alias@@uiuc.edu)	350-399
# 1	newline character		400
#
# Start with
# dd if=rmt0 of=fac ibs=4000 cbs=400 conv=ascii
#
# some definitions
#

#
